      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently maintained, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. The exterior looks great with a nice gloss, though you'll notice some light surface scratches and a few minor rock chips on the front bumper from regular highway use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, showing only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smooth and shifts well, with all major features and electronics functioning as they should. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that is ready for the road.",
