      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and remains a functional option for daily transportation. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable paint chips, scratches, and a few small dings across the body panels. Inside, the upholstery exhibits significant wear and some staining, though all essential controls and features remain operational. While it has been well-maintained mechanically to ensure reliability, buyers should expect the typical aesthetic imperfections associated with a car of this age and mileage.",
